        "content": "<p><a href=\"https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Automated_edits/Latvia-bot/Addresses\">Wiki</a> has ir covered. See under</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Beside buildings and address points, address tags are also assigned to objects listed in <a href=\"https://github.com/Davis-Klavins/osm-latvia-bot/blob/main/tags_4_addresses.csv\">tags_4_addresses.csv</a> (amenities, shops, offices etc.)</p>\n</blockquote>",
